    <p>4</p>
    <p>En­ter Un­dead Arena at Sun­tec City by Zero La­tency, which of­fers multi-player vir­tual-re­al­ity gam­ing ex­pe­ri­ences.</p>
    <p>Your mis­sion is to bat­tle zom­bies in front of a blood­thirsty crowd presided by a game-show host. You may need to re­call lessons learnt from The Hunger Games (2012 to 2015) and Train To Bu­san (2016) films.</p>
    <p>Go with four friends a ses­sion as Covid-19 re­stric­tions ap­ply, even in zom­bie war­fare.</p>
    <p>Use promo code “YAYNEWGAME” for a 30 per cent dis­count on on­line book­ings till Aug 14. For ex­am­ple, an off-peak ticket of $48 is now $33.60.</p>
    <p>ze­ro­la­ten­cyvr.com/sin­ga­pore/book-now</p>
